 The positive CD has the following information: Sigh No More — close‑miked, vocal‑forward folk‑rock with warm, revealing midrange, tactile micro‑dynamics and preserved headroom. Modest compression, restrained processing, tight supporting harmonies, punchy acoustic rhythms and sparse accents keep lyrics and phrase‑forward lead front‑and‑center.. 
