 The positive CD has the following information: harmony‑forward, glistening three‑part blends and jangly midrange guitars; immediate top‑end sheen balanced with roomy reverb and tasteful compression. Stacked harmonies lift and color the lead without burying it; sequencing emphasizes interplay and melodic clarity—suitable for listeners who favor lush harmonic beds and tactile, breathy vocal presence.. 
